# Generated files (`*.g.cs`)

These files include `// <auto-generated />` and `ManifestSha256` headers.

**Do not use Write/StrReplace on this file.** Change the manifest under `pipeline/raylib6/`, then:

```bash
dotnet run --project codegen/Novolis.Raylib.CodeGen -- generate
```

If the task is only consumer/sample code, use public APIs in `Novolis.Raylib.Runtime` (`Graphics`, `World`, `Hud`, `Gui`) — not raw `Raylib6Native`.
